# ============================================
# El Bahrawy Advertising - Environment Variables
# ============================================

# DATABASE - Required for Vercel deployment
# Get a free PostgreSQL database from:
#   - Supabase: https://supabase.com (recommended)
#   - Neon: https://neon.tech
#   - Railway: https://railway.app
#
# Replace the URL below with your PostgreSQL connection string
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://username:password@host:5432/database_name?schema=public"

# ============================================
# How to deploy on Vercel:
# ============================================
# 1. Create a free database at https://supabase.com
#    - Go to Project Settings > Database
#    - Copy the "Connection string" (URI format)
#    - Replace YOUR-PASSWORD with your actual password
#
# 2. Push to GitHub:
#    - git init && git add . && git commit -m "initial"
#    - git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR-USER/el-bahrawy.git
#    - git push -u origin main
#
# 3. Deploy on Vercel:
#    - Go to https://vercel.com > New Project
#    - Import your GitHub repo
#    - Add environment variable:
#      DATABASE_URL = your PostgreSQL connection string
#    - Click "Deploy"
#
# 4. After first deploy, seed the database:
#    - Go to https://vercel.com > your project > Settings > Functions
#    - Visit: https://your-domain.vercel.app/api/seed
#    - This creates all categories, products, and sample orders
# ============================================
